wardance.walk_of_dionysus.desc:
You may equip up to 3 colors. 
All stuns against you are upgraded to knockdowns. Fall down drunk when knocked down, creating a shockwave that deals 5 posture damage to enemies in a 5 block radius. 
{Automatically consume 1 might whenever possible to immediately inflict knockdown on yourself and stand back up.; YELLOW}

wardance.suplex.desc:
造成大量{架勢傷害; UNDERLINE; 等於150%自身當前架勢}。
若目標被擊倒則額外增加一個破綻，並造成衝擊波對5方塊內的的{敵人; ITALIC; wardance.skill.enemies}造成{架勢傷害; UNDERLINE; 溢出架勢傷害的50%}。
{施放此技能會消耗自身幾乎所有架勢; RED}

wardance.overbear.desc:
架勢傷害翻倍
{破防目標時將其擊倒並額外添加一個破綻; DARK_GREEN}.
{破防失敗時使你的副手進入5秒冷卻; RED}
